Life Story

 

Purpose: to accompany Nólora during her journey to Azadmere, as an emissary of Melderyn and ally of Emelrene; ...to serve asNólora’s translator and advisor.

Church of Save-K’nor: Laity (God of knowledge, tricks, and jest).

Blessing bonus: Folklore.

Arcane talent: Elemental Bolt (Aura). You can invoke as a 1-turn action and target an entity within 70 feet and LOS. If successful,the target must test Spirit; for each step-loss, it suffers Aural Shock 1.

Arcane talent: Sensitivity. You can sense arcane energy within 35 feet. A free passive roll by the GM can give you a very generalidea or hunch. You can then actively invoke as a 1-round action to gain more details.
